198
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:35,820
Now, if you brought it in
on the side of V as a number

199
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:37,850
it would go in just
like the number.

200
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:40,230
If you bring it
into the left side,

201
00:14:40,230 --> 00:14:43,200
remember it's
conjugate homogeneous,

202
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,750
so this enters as
