203
00:14:45,750 --> 00:15:05,730
So this would be e1, Phi of
e1 star times V plus en, Phi

204
00:15:05,730 --> 00:15:23,240
of en star, v. And then we have
our result that this Phi of v

205
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:25,050
